title: ArtyTorrent Pack 54-Progressive Electro House 120-129bpm-WAV
description:
ArtyTorrent Pack 54-Progressive Electro House 120-129bpm-WAV
------------------------------------------------------------

Electro house is hot right now. It seems like a natural progression from so called "Progressive" House to me. Certainly, the drum loops in this pack suit either genre, plus many more besides. The 4/4 beats should work nicely in any electronic house production, be it techno, trance or minimal. The tempo range is 120-129 bpm.

Torrent contains 5 RAR files with 263 loops
-------------------------------------------
Chicago Fire Prog Electro House 120-129 (101 loops)
Ghetto Electro House 120-129 (137 loops)
Machine Language House 120-129 (6 loops)
Misc Electro House (12 loops)
VMH1 Minimal Beats 128 (7 loops)

All samples have, as usual, been normalized and acidized and are 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz, looped precisely and containing the approx bpm in the filenames.

The samples are from a variety of sources including CDs produced by EastWest, Sonic Foundry/Sony, Tekniks and Vengeance.

--
Arty - "Electronic progression"
13th February 2008.

P.S. This is my last pack for today. I should be uploading again tomorrow, but only if a couple of new downloaders leave "thankyou" comments, so sign up and join TPB now if you haven&#039;t already. :P
